data.chText: 十年，十年期（尤指一个年代）
data.enText: a period of ten years, especially a period such as 1910–1919 or 1990–1999

simple_means.memory_skill: dec 十 + ade 某种行动的个人或集体 → 十年

tr: the cardinal number that is the sum of nine and one
the base of the decimal system

value.def: A decade is a period of ten years, especially one that begins with a year ending in 0, for example 1980 to 1989.

example.ex: ...the last decade of the nineteenth century.

value.tran: 十年，十年期（尤指一个年代)

trans: 近十年来；在过去的十年中；在过去的十年里
